reviewText: I like my Baton twirling book. Came in handy when I was relearning my twirls. I should have ordered the 2nd book instead but it worked.
I love this ! Gave me everything to Lead the Parade! I will get her whole collection! She is easy to follow, and makes everything easy to understand and perform

My granddaughter was not interested in the video. She had never expressed an interest in twirling, so that may
have been the reason.
